personalInfo.name: Ryan A. Ellis
personalInfo.title: Data Analyst & AI Engineer
personalInfo.summary: Experienced Data Analyst with 3+ years of expertise in AI/ML solutions, statistical analysis, and automation. Proven track record of delivering measurable business impact through innovative data science applications, including 60% time reduction in classification tasks and 30% improvement in data processing efficiency. Specializes in NLP, machine learning model deployment, and enterprise automation solutions.
